				\begin{document}$${(T_x)}$$\end{document} of the glass samples. Raman spectra were recorded with a Renishaw inVia spectrometer coupled with a Leica DM2700 microscope with 633 nm laser excitation. Optical absorption spectra of the glass were recorded on UV-2500 (SHIMADZU) and NIR (BRUKER MPA—Multi Purpose Analyzer) spectrophotometers. Luminescence measurements were performed on Florolog3-iHR HORIBA fluorescence spectrometer upon 443 nm excitation. Density of the glass samples were estimated with distilled water as immersion liquid by Archimedes’ method. All the measurements were conducted at room temperature.

